# CLAUDE.local.md — Template

> [!warning] This file overrides CLAUDE.md and is gitignored.
> Use it to attach **your** private context to a local clone — personal conventions, your infra topology, credentials references (not values), the parent stack you integrate with. Nothing here is shipped to the public repo.

Copy this file to `.claude/CLAUDE.local.md` and edit as you see fit. Claude Code loads both `CLAUDE.md` (public) and `CLAUDE.local.md` (private) — the local one takes precedence on overlaps.

