|---|---|---|
| — | — | — |

## Parent Stack / Registry

- Parent project context file :: `<path>`
- Project registry :: `<path>`

## Personal Conventions

- Git remote alias :: `<origin | gitea | fork>`
- Preferred editor :: `<vscode | vim | zed>`
- Shell :: `<bash | zsh | fish | pwsh>`

## Credential References (NAMES ONLY — never values)

- Stripe live key :: stored in `<secret manager path>`
- Anthropic API key :: stored in `<secret manager path>`
- Postgres root :: stored in `<secret manager path>`

## Notes Claude should remember

Add anything you want Claude to treat as permanent context for this clone — e.g. "prefer French replies", "always run `gitnexus_impact` even on trivial edits", "default deploy target is my KVM-at-home".
